description: A "Rave Cave" party in the Norwegian capital Oslo leaves 25 people in need of hospital treatment.
title: Coronavirus: Norway bunker partygoers poisoned by carbon monoxide
title_page: Coronavirus: Norway bunker partygoers poisoned by carbon monoxide - BBC News
maintext: The lives of all of the victims, believed to be mainly aged between 20 and 30, are said to be out of danger but police have called for other attendees to seek medical attention if they start suffering from nausea, headaches or dizziness.
